### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health

### Trigger OSINT cycle
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cycle/run

### Get cycle status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cycle/status

### Latest signals
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/signals/latest?limit=10

### Latest intelligence records
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/intelligence/latest?limit=10

### Latest brief
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/brief/latest

### Brief index
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/brief/index

### Trigger quant cycle
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/quant/cycle/run

### Quant status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/quant/status

### Open investigation case
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/workspace/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Investigation",
  "question": "What are we investigating?",
  "tags": ["tag1", "tag2"]
}

### List open cases
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/workspace/cases

### Engage kill switch
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/kill

### Clear kill switch
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/kill
